name: Community Halloween on the Blockchain
description: This NFT was created for the first ever HEN Happy Halloween Community Event that will run Oct 27th - Nov 1st and will only be for sale on primary during that time period.  To participate in the event mint an OBJKT with 5 to 250 edition with the hashtag #HENHalloween in the Hic Et Nunc tags (right there below this area) and SWAP (drop, price) it on October 27th!
